@startuml
title Client Error Normalization Opt-In (After)
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam ArrowColor #111111
skinparam defaultFontColor #111111
skinparam defaultFontName Consolas

actor "SDK Consumer" as Consumer #D6EAF8
component "createClient(..., {\n  experimental: {\n    enableErrorNormalization: true\n  }\n})" as Client #D5F5E3
component "Result Formatter\n(createResultFormatter)" as Formatter #F9E79F
component "normalizeAthenaError(result, context?)" as Normalize #FDEBD0
component "AthenaResult<T>\n{ data, error, status, ... }" as Result #E8DAEF
component "Hidden metadata\n__athenaNormalizedError" as Metadata #F5CBA7

Consumer --> Client : opt-in once
Client --> Formatter : inject into from/rpc/query paths
Formatter --> Result : preserve AthenaResult shape
Formatter --> Normalize : pre-compute with table/operation
Normalize --> Metadata : produce normalized envelope
Metadata --> Result : attach non-enumerable metadata
Consumer --> Normalize : normalizeAthenaError(result)
Normalize --> Consumer : reuse attached metadata

note right of Result
No public input/output type changes.
Existing AthenaResult contract remains intact.
end note
@enduml
